name: Goodybag
long_description:
Goodybag helps you find catering for your office. Easily search restaurants and have food delivered to your next meeting.

For Restaurants and Caterers:
Goodybag lists your catering menu with no startup or monthly fees. You set your own delivery fees and zones. 

For Businesses:
Goodybag is an easy, time-saving way for you to explore and order food from restaurants around town for your employees.
